==English==
===Etymology===
[[Blend]] of '''[[w:Scarborough, Ontario|Scarborough]]''' and '''[[w:Harlem|Harlem]]'''
[[Category:Portmanteaus|scarlem]]

===Proper noun===
'''Scarlem'''

#(''derogatory slang'') An area east of [[Toronto]] in [[Canada]], known for its poor [[neighbourhood]]s and youth [[gang]]s, by comparison with Harlem in [[New York]].